OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThailand's lese-majeste law
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fexplained                  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thailand's lese-majeste law, which     
OL,6, forbids the insult of the monarchy, is 
OL,7, among the strictest in the world.      
OL,9,FIt has been increasingly enforced ever 
OL,10,Fsince the Thai military took power in  
OL,11,F2014 in a coup, and many people have   
OL,12,Fbeen punished with harsh jail          
OL,13,Fsentences.                             
OL,15,FCritics say the military-backed        
OL,16,Fgovernment uses the law to clamp down  
OL,17,Fon free speech, and the United Nations 
OL,18,Fhas repeatedly called on Thailand to   
OL,19,Famend it.                              
